Oh the Irony of August Snow...

"I need to step back and breath in order to be clear and persistant about what I want but I demand, put down, and burrow my fears behind frusterated words."

So I really DO understand where others are coming from in saying that somtimes I have a negative attitude... because I do, but everone dose some time or a nother as well..  I just hate being judgted on asumtions.. or having others put me down with out knowing me..

Weather it was a joke or someone thinking I needed a reality check, The simple act of putting that pamphlet in my box hurt me a lot..

It feel like its dumb for me to justify myself in this situation, but here it goes..


the majority of the negative comments that come out of my moth are eather from pure scarcasim, or me attempting to start a coNversation when noting else is there to be said..  sometimes my negative words are in some way a sign of me putting effort towards somthing with the mask of negativity..

The past few moths has given me time to realize why I do the things that I do...

If you want to know somthing...ask me..
PLEASE
instead of asuming

GIVE ME A CHANCE
(LOVE)
I want to kill you.. slowly but surly.. I want to FUCKING KILL YOU OMG!

So I havnt been on LJ in FOREVER.  Things/my life has been insane.. School is going great.  My last day of finals is on tuesday.. (yay!)  I did my scene last friday.. thank GOD thats over and I feel like it went really well.. :)

PS:  I'm working at a tanning salon :D (In Mercer Island..)  its annoying because the salon have like 3 locations in Seattle.. but am I wokring there? no..  Its great though cuz I really enjoy the people that I work with and the atmisphere (pluse the free tanning is amazing..  its nice because working here is pushing me to high maitnence again (which is a good thing) I'm getting my eye borws shaped and waxed for free next weeks and I'm getting my nails back for half the price.. mm yummy!  Pluse theres a lady that come in here that dose amazing mink lashes that I would end up paying nearly nothing for... mmmm delicious!  I'm prety sure I'll end up working most of Christmas break.. tis lovly!

So I'm having an issue....  As of recently my mind has been consumed of thoughts of what might happen and assumption... its gotten really bad...  now when ever the though crosses my mind I feel sick to my stomack... I literally feel as though I'm going to throw up...  this has become I constant thing... I dont know what to do.. but I realized just waiting it out dosnt help.... FUCK fuck FUCK!

I cant love you...  
But I do.. ehhhhhhhhh!
I dont know how much longer I can do this...

I can learn to open up more... I slowly am..
but one thing will never change...
It will always be me and only me..
I can only rely  on and trust in myself..

everyone else has failed me..
I want you... I want you so bad.. so bad its driving me mad.....

Oddly I have not posted anything since I've moved in or started school.  Things have been crazy.  Cornish is amazing and absolutely perfect for me.  My classes are helping me be more calm and have a better sense of who I am and what I'm doing..  Everyday is a new adventure and I love it..  I picked up a new book at Bailey/Coy that has been inspiring the shit out of me.. :P    Its about Zen Koans and how everything is nothing...

"How much  do you do for praise?  How many things do you say just to make an impression on others.  What are you really achieving when you try to make an impression? And how many accounts do you have to keep?  If you didn't do things for merit and advancement, or if you didn't act with motives at all, what would life be like?  At work? In bed? Alone in a room?  Even alone in a room you can be consumed with wanting others to see you in a good light.  Can you imagine how things would be different with out that kind of wanting?" - John Tarrant

I realize how much time I spend waiting... waiting waiting for someone to be impressed by me, fall in love with me, for others to view me in a certain light, for opportunities to come my way...  When I wan something asking dose nothing.  I am ether asking or waiting..  I want to lean how to sub consciously wait and want.  That way I really be expecting anything or be disappointed if I dont get what I want.

Deep in my eyes, what do you see?
Deep in my sighs, listen to me.... please

I've forgotten about myself
I've forgotten about who I am and what I want
this isnt me..

(Im scared.... for reasons only I will know.. :/)
"eww theres gay people going to cornish?" -Eoin

shit fuck shit!  
I'm sooo dumb
I HATE this! :/

WOW... do you not notice at ALL!?!?!  (I honestly doubt that I'm this good at hiding my emotions/feelings.)

To bad you were right.. (alcohol is my vice... :/ )

God Damn!  I just about had a heat attack!  NO one saw that right? lol
Whatever.. I'm fucking amazing! :P
"I agree, you don't want a commitment, you just want people to touch you.."  -Rachel

I ordered my dress online a few days and and they said it would take 3-4 weeks for the dress to arive..
My mom gets an e-mail from the company she ordered the dress from saying the company dosnt make the dress anymore... OMG  

First of all I havent  found a nother dress that I EVEN like, let alone LOVE like I love this one... ehh So I'm in a fucking panic trying to find a dress that isnt even being made anymore in a size 12...  

I'm fucking NERVOUS!! : /

So basically everyone is insane!  This weekend was amazing! Seussical ended.  Saterday nigh was the last time I  would ever perform on stage at ARHS... (Such an amazing feeling!)   That night was my best show by far! I feels so odd to be done with high school drama...  I'm not even part of that anymore I've spent the last 6 year being in shows that Mrs. Seman has dericted and I'll never being in her shows anymore...  

I'm soooo ot even here anymore...  In my mind I'm already in Seattle.. (God! I cant Wait!!!)

In other news I have a big mouth...  Anyone who knows me even the slighest bit knows NOT to tell me ANYTHING! lol (unless you one of a select few..)

My Story:
Saterday night after the show we had a cast party...  This girl(who was in the show) decided to tell me that she had sex with one of the techs.  She said it happened 3 times, all wail the show was going on.. OMG Are you dumb!?!  You dont tell ME somthing like this!  Of corse I told eveyone... :X  MS. Seman found out and the guy will most likly lose his job.  I honestly dont know if she told me just to get attention or if it was realy true.. meh eather way its sad...  Hella shit is going down!

Dance tonight?  I'm sure it will be amazing! <3

I'm tired of fucking having to clear my name for
SHIT THAT I DIDNT DO!
(story of my life..)

We had teasers today..
I walked around school with my big ass tail looking like a fool.. 
All day I felt like I was dieing...
I belive I have strep maybe? 
I got home from school, slept, ate and will most likly end up going 2 bed @ 8 or 9 or somthing..
God I'm lame!
meh.. this shall be fun..

Call me? <3

EVERYTHING in my life runs on a cycle.. and sometimes these vicious cycles cross paths..

I've realized its not even woth it...  the tought of it seams nice for the time being but what would I get out of it? 

NOTHING!(thats not who I am and I'm not going to let myself become that person..)



No matter what I do I feel as though I'm being jugdged 24/7....even by my closest friends.

You dont have to know me very well to know that I'm scarcastic about ALMOST all of the negative things that I say...  (I dont belive its hard to comprehend that...)  But I honestly just cant fathem how people dont see that or at least understand it a little...  its sooooo blatently obivious!  

Its bugs me when people think that thats all that I'm about.. *Scarcasim and shit talking*  when realy I chose not to show EVERYONE 100% of who I am.. 

I guess I hide behind my scarcasim because its hard for me to trust people..  But would you honestly blame me with all the shit that has happened in the past few years?

In other news Seussical opens tonight!
Info: March 15th, 16th, 17th, 22nd, 23rd, & 24th
@ 7:30 PM 
Tickets are $9.00 for adults, $7.00 for students/seniors

Come see me?  <3

So I called today...

They havent accapted/processed any of the theatre apps.. AT ALL

My admission councler said he would call the theatre department and then call me back...

blaaaaaaaa fuck you for not telling me today and making me wait!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

(I stayed home from 1st and 2nd p so I could call and I'm having massive troble being motivated to get ready.. wach me not even go to school today...)

For the first time in a long time I was achally able to vocalize my thoughts behind *ish* wail still making sense.. HORRAY!

*yay for vague LJ posts!*

Today is gonna be a LONG day..

I have about 50 BILLION things on my mind..

I cant excape my life.. ( not even when I dream) god damnit!

I have a secret..
Achally I told two people...
OH MY GOD!

I'm a bad person...

I should prolby be gone already but I'm to lazy to leave..  I've been thinking a lot about the lack of drama in my life.. and I came to the comclusion that the drama that my life has perviously consisted of, I started..  Its been ME!  not the other people around me..  Am I growing?  Am I talking a step to being about that? 

WOW.. last year I would have said that I LIVE for drama and confliction.. but now.. I live for me... 

horray!

hmm I think I deserve starbucks and fatty food as a reward! :P

-It feels odd to get encourgment and be told that someone has 100% faith in you from people that a look up to.. its make me relize that I need to  stop relying on others and start relying on myself..  Latly I've been putting my trust in other to make me happy and thats not the way it should be.  I shouldnt needs others to make me happy...  I NEED me to make me feel better.  Its funny because most of the encourgment I get from others is quite obiviously bs... My life is blan right now and I'm ready for it to go back to the crazy rolarcoaster ride.. : )

*There hasent been a single day where I HAVENT thought about what will happen with my college situation.. blaaaa I have NO patience..*
There are certain things that your NOT soupose to tell a person... and that would be one of them.. blaaa
So durring my childrens theatre show some idiot dug through my pruse and stole my Ipod.... EHHHHHH!!!
Somehow the secrects we have kept are know by other.....

One again this weekend was absoutly amazing!  In the begaining I was hesitant about doing the show, but I'm realy glad I did. : )  I love just being able to be "me" when I'm hanging out with friends.. I havent been able to do that in a long time, I dont think I've realy felt comfertable With a lot of people up unitl now..  I know I say "thanks for being wonderful" a lot, but I realy do mean it... : ) 

 Somthing has changed with in me, somthing is not the same..


Saterday is my Cornish Audition...  I'm scared shitless.. I'm never scared shitless.  Blaa  I hope I'm prepared enough,  I hope I dont fuck up, I hope I do good, I hope I get in, I hope I get a talent based scolarship.   I hope.....

Thinking about the feature scares me.. a lot

So I went to work three hours ago and the weather was completly fine.. no snow, no ice, nada!  Two hours into work we had to close early.. the was 6 goddamn inches of show on my car and such..  I proceded to drive home... I was fine untill I got to the entrence of lakeland hills..There were about 20 cars stoped in every wich way..  Me being the idiot that I am thought that I would be able to get up the hill and home... I had no such luck  I spune out a few times and ran into the side walk (where at the moment my car still sits)  Some guy that I used to go to chuch with was drive behind me...(I was so thankful)  Now I"m home and warm.. and some what happy lol..  I'm just nervous that the weather will stay bad and make the sho be cancled.. :/ rar I hate the show..  
Snow snow go away...



-Paris Hilton definatly makes me feel better when I'm in a bad mood.. :)
Hella Sexy!

Last weekend was pretty much amazing!!!  Friday was opening night of Seussical and 30mins before the show started the power went off...  The power never came back on and we had to cancel the show wich sucked cuz everyone's energy was so high..  So Instead I ate and continued to be a photo whore with Eoin.. *So much fun!*   Last weekends shows went great but I am so warn out... I havent had time to just stop and breath...  There for I'm not at school today...  My voice is COMPLETELY gone and I'm hoping it come back before friday.. : /  I have so much I need to acomplish in the next few days and I'm scared it wont get it gone...  Once I finish everything I can let lose... and god knows how much I need that... :P
Check) - I'm amazing

I am starting to relize that this shit always happens to me..  It has started to bug me less and less... 
even though every one in a wile I want to ball my eyes out...

Caitlin's show is tonight and I'm extremly excited... It feels like its been forever sence I've been to Issaquh but its only been a week or so.  Lets see, flowers, chocolates, camra, and frumpay shirt.. I think I'm good!  PIcture to come!
